name: RespiratoryFailureAcuteOrChronicI9
title: Respiratory failure acute or chronic I9
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains diagnoses most commonly used for patients with acute or chronic respiratory failure.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who have an active  diagnosis of acute or chronic respiratory failure. Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element will map to the Diagnosis category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Include codes representing an active diagnosis of  acute or chronic respiratory failure using the  ICD 9 CM code system.),(Exclusion Criteria: Codes that do not meet the inclusion criteria should be excluded.)
